module.field: By enabling the interrupt handler, Grace generates a fully working interrupt service routine in InterruptVectors_init.c file inside src folder. User could insert code inside the specified area of the ISR and the code is preserved. When a user disables the interrupt handler, the user's inserted code remains at the bottom of the file which is automatically re-inserted if the user re-enables the interrupt handler. User could also manually remove the code when it is no longer needed.
